### Subir una foto ---->FALTA
POST http://localhost:3000/api/comercios/contenido/fotos HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="photo"; filename="shishaBar.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpg

< ./shishaBar.jpg
--boundary--

###Borrar foto ---->FALTA
